[screaming continues]

835
00:42:44.103 --> 00:42:46.105
[Jun-hyeong whimpers]

836
00:42:47.565 --> 00:42:48.691
[Jun-hyeong groans]

837
00:42:49.900 --> 00:42:51.902
[whimpers]

838
00:42:53.487 --> 00:42:56.532
